<div class="container page">

<h1>Welcome</h1>
  <article class="entry-content">
    <p class="lead">
      This blog is about <a href="https://blog.glyphdrawing.club/usage-tutorial-for-glyph-drawing-club">Glyph Drawing Club</a>, modular design, ASCII art, text art, typography, type design, HTML & CSS, programming and other curious things.
    </p>
